inherit kde-v4
   require alsa-lib bzip2 cmake e2fsprogs giflib libXpm libXtst lua pcre shared-mime-info soprano strigi
  optional aspell  '' '' for spell checking 
  optional avahi   '' '' for zero conf support
  optional enchant '' '' for spell checking
  optional gamin   '' '' for file system change notification
  optional jasper  '' '' for jpeg 2000 support
  optional openexr '' '' for HDR image file format support
  optional openssl '' '' for secure socket layer support
  optional soprano '' '' to build nepomuk for semantic desktop

    ignore 'orig'
  category development
# hspell website is missing 20080116
#            'hspell:::for Hebrew spell checking support'
  estimate 60000
      desc 'kdelibs-v4 contains the base applications that form the core of KDE.
kdelibs contains the base applications that form the core of
the K Desktop Environment like the window manager, the terminal
emulator, the control center, the file manager, and the panel.'
